575
00:42:09,122 --> 00:42:11,424
Pensaban que era...

576
00:42:11,490 --> 00:42:12,700
EL CÓMICO ANÓNIMO
DEL SHOW DEL GONG

577
00:42:12,931 --> 00:42:14,425
